Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.41,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfektné počasie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:07.66,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? To...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.14,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.08,TOA10h,,0000,0000,0000,,Trochu som pribrala...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:15.24,TOA10h,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.54,TOA10h,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmiem sa pozerať.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:18.30,TOA10h,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale... Ách...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.10,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedokážem odvrátiť zrak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.24,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.53,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto sú asi spomienky Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:26.57,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:30.07,TOA10,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Počkaj, Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:38.30,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Rozpáľ ma
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:38.30,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}watashi yo moete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:46.89,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Rozpáľ ma v objatí. Nie je hriechom pokúsiť sa ma objať, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:46.89,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}moete dakishimete miru no wa tsumi jyanai desshou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:48.77,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Prečistiť temnotu ohňom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:48.77,OPka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}himei yami wo harae
